description:
UFO 50 is a collection of 50 single and multiplayer games from the creators of Spelunky, Downwell, Air Land & Sea,
Skorpulac, Catacomb Kids, and Madhouse.
Jump in and explore a variety of genres, from platformers and shoot 'em ups to puzzle games and RPGs.
Our goal is to combine a familiar 8-bit aesthetic with new ideas and modern game design sensibilities.

0.1.0.title: UFO 50 APWorld 0.1.0

0.1.1.description:
Loosened the Unimplemented Games restriction a little bit.
You can now choose the following unimplemented games without the host.yaml warning: Ninpek, Magic Garden, Velgress, and Waldorf's Journey
You can now do a game that is only unimplemented games.
Be warned that unimplemented means the only checks are Garden, Gold, and (optionally) Cherry. They can take considerably longer to get checks than in the implemented games. Don't bring something like that to a sync unless you know what you're doing.

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/UFO-50-Archipelago/Archipelago/compare/0.1.0...0.1.1
